  "description": "<i>Ko?o Fortuny II</i> is a game loosely based on the TV show Wheel of Fortune. The players take turns guessing letters to form a word or a saying. The game can be played with up to three players. Computer players can be defined by two difficulty levels. During their turn the players can spin the wheel, guess a consonant, buy a vowel or guess the password. <br><br>The game features text based graphics with no sound or music.\n",
